extendedInfo.description: This free fishing times app offers easy to read solunar fishing times, day ratings, tide times, sun and moon information to increase your fishing success.The free version is ad supported and limited to 3 days forecast.This application is powered by http://www.fishingreminder.comSolunar Clock:- Green Bars indicate good major and minor fishing times (major longer, minor shorter bar)- Blue Bars indicate low and high tide times.- Center indicates moonphase- Gray current time indicator- top right of screen has a day rating indicator ( 1-4 fishes, fair to excellent )- sun and moon icons for sun/moon rise and setPlease email me if you have any suggestions for further improvements!tight lines to all !!!KW: best fishing times, fishing calendar, fishing tables, solunar tables,  solunar chart, lunar fishing calendar, tide tables, tide times

reviews.title: Really great fishing resource
reviews.comment: I found only small issues with the auto-detect location, however manually setting the location is really easy so not a major drama for me.  I recommend this to anybody looking for a basic fishing resource tool.  Works great!
reviews.author: Sam Hansen

reviews.title: Calendar issues
reviews.comment: The free version doesn\'t allow you to go past the current month.  On the last two days of the month you only have 1day or 2 at most as the calendar set up won\'t allow you to click over to the first of the next month.   Otherwise works well
reviews.author: michael sorrensen

reviews.title: Hmmm
reviews.comment: I stay 4km from the sea, but the app insists to get data from a station 100km inland. No tide station there. Would like to be able to select my own station.

reviews.title: Couldn\'t believe it
reviews.comment: This actually works, no doubt about it. I am a novice and usually never catch anything so I tried this app and waited for an excellent day and I had caught my first fish and had tons of big bites that got away.
